sequenceDiagram
  autonumber

  participant U as User (Browser)
  participant SPA as Stitch Web App (SPA)
  participant IDP as SSO IdP (Entra ID / Okta)
  participant AUTH as Auth Broker (Amazon Cognito)
  participant API as Stitch API (Backend)
  participant DB as Tenant DB (Brand/User/Roles)

  Note over U,SPA: User clicks "Sign in with Microsoft/Okta"
  U->>SPA: Start SSO
  SPA->>AUTH: /oauth2/authorize (PKCE)
  AUTH->>IDP: Redirect (SAML/OIDC)

  Note over IDP: Enforce corporate policies\n(MFA, conditional access, device posture)
  IDP-->>AUTH: Auth response (code/assertion)
  AUTH-->>SPA: Redirect to /auth/callback?code=...
  SPA->>AUTH: Exchange code for tokens
  AUTH-->>SPA: ID token + access token (JWT)

  SPA->>API: Call /me (JWT)
  API->>AUTH: Validate JWT (JWKS)
  AUTH-->>API: Token valid

  API->>DB: Lookup user by (tenantId, idpSubject/email)
  alt First-time user
    API->>DB: Create Brand/Tenant (partition key)
    API->>DB: Create User profile (name, email)
    API->>DB: Create Membership (role=Owner)
  else Returning user
    API->>DB: Update lastLoginAt, displayName if changed
  end

  API-->>SPA: 200 OK (profile + role + sidebar config)
  SPA-->>U: Render App Shell + Account Overview

